Name: lorenz_phase_space
Version: 0.0.1
Summary: Visualization tool designed to analyze and illustrate the Lorenz Energy Cycle for atmospheric science.
Author: Danilo Couto de Souza
Author-email: danilo.oceano@gmail.com
